# Keep the Docker build context tiny: the image only needs the two CCF setup
# scripts (COPYed explicitly in the Dockerfile). Everything else is mounted at
# runtime. Docker requires each parent directory to be un-ignored to reach a
# nested file after a `*` exclude.
*
!third_party
third_party/*
!third_party/CCF
third_party/CCF/*
!third_party/CCF/scripts
third_party/CCF/scripts/*
!third_party/CCF/scripts/setup-ci.sh
!third_party/CCF/scripts/setup-dev.sh
